SUMMARY:Splat Space Board meeting
DESCRIPTION:Splat Space - Durham's Hackerspace\nOn the last Tuesday of eac
 h month we hold our board meeting. This meeting is a chance for Splat Spac
 e's board to meet and discuss what will be on the meeting agenda for the M
 ember Meeting\, which is held on the 1st Tuesday of each month.\n\nThis me
 eting is usually held in person at Splat Space.\n\nGoogle Meet Video Call:
 \n[https://meet.google.com/usc-eavv-jkc](https://meet.google.com/usc-eavv-
 jkc)
