SUMMARY:Splat Space Member meeting
DESCRIPTION:Splat Space - Durham's Hackerspace\nOn the first Tuesday of ev
 ery month\, we hold our Member Meeting. This meeting is an opportunity for
  the Splat Space board to update the members on events\, issues and news r
 elated to Splat Space.\n\nWhile the majority of our members attend in pers
 on and we encourage them to do so\, we stream the meeting using Google Mee
 t for those who want to attend remotely.\n\nClick this link attend the mee
 ting online.\n\n[https://meet.google.com/usc-eavv-jkc](https://meet.google
 .com/usc-eavv-jkc)
